" \w* \w  Shimeah .  |strong="8093" srcloc="WLC:2SA.13.3.6" \w* \f + \fr 13.3 \ft "Shimeah" is a variant of "Shammah", "Shimea", and "Shimei"; see 1 Samuel 16:9, 2 Samuel 21:21, and 1 Chronicles 2:13. \f* \w  Jonadab  |strong="3122" srcloc="WLC:2SA.13.3.9" \w* \w  was a very  |strong="3966" srcloc="WLC:2SA.13.3.12" \w* \w  shrewd  |strong="2450" srcloc="WLC:2SA.13.3.11" \w* \w  man ,  |strong="376" srcloc="WLC:2SA.13.3.10" \w* \v 4 \w  so he asked  |strong="559" srcloc="WLC:2SA.13.4.1" \w* \w  [Amnon] ,  |srcloc="WLC:2SA.13.4.2" \w* \w  “ Why  |strong="4069" srcloc="WLC:2SA.13.4.3" \w* \w  are you ,  |strong="859" srcloc="WLC:2SA.13.4.4" \w* \w  the son  |strong="1121" srcloc="WLC:2SA.13.4.7" \w* \w  of the king ,  |strong="4428" srcloc="WLC:2SA.13.4.8" \w* \w  so  |strong="3602" srcloc="WLC:2SA.13.4.5" \w* \w  depressed  |strong="1800" srcloc="WLC:2SA.13.4.6" \w* \w  morning  |strong="1242" srcloc="WLC:2SA.13.4.9" \w* \w  after morning ?  |strong="1242" srcloc="WLC:2SA.13.4.10" \w* \w  Won’t  |strong="3808" srcloc="WLC:2SA.13.4.11" \w* \w  you tell  |strong="5046" srcloc="WLC:2SA.13.4.12" \w* \w  me ? ”  |srcloc="WLC:2SA.13.4.13" \w* \w  Amnon  |strong="550" srcloc="WLC:2SA.13.4.16" \w* \w  replied  |strong="559" srcloc="WLC:2SA.13.4.14" \w* \w  ,  |srcloc="WLC:2SA.13.4.15" \w* \w  “ I am  |strong="589" srcloc="WLC:2SA.13.4.22" \w* \w  in love  |strong="157" srcloc="WLC:2SA.13.4.23" \w* \w  with Tamar ,  |strong="8559" srcloc="WLC:2SA.13.4.18" \w* \w  my brother  |strong="251" srcloc="WLC:2SA.13.4.21" \w* \w  Absalom’s  |strong="53" srcloc="WLC:2SA.13.4.20" \w* \w  sister . ”  |strong="269" srcloc="WLC:2SA.13.4.19" \w* \v 5 \w  Jonadab  |strong="3082" srcloc="WLC:2SA.13.5.3" \w* \w  told  |strong="559" srcloc="WLC:2SA.13.5.1" \w* \w  him ,  |srcloc="WLC:2SA.13.5.2" \w* \w  “ Lie down  |strong="7901" srcloc="WLC:2SA.13.5.4" \w* \w  on  |strong="5921" srcloc="WLC:2SA.13.5.5" \w* \w  your bed  |strong="4904" srcloc="WLC:2SA.13.5.6" \w* \w  and pretend you are ill .  |