" srcloc="WLC:2SA.21.4.8" \w* \w  Saul  |strong="7586" srcloc="WLC:2SA.21.4.9" \w* \w  or  |strong="5973" srcloc="WLC:2SA.21.4.10" \w* \w  his house ,  |strong="1004" srcloc="WLC:2SA.21.4.11" \w* \w  nor  |strong="369" srcloc="WLC:2SA.21.4.12" \w* \w  should you  |strong="376" srcloc="WLC:2SA.21.4.14" \w* \w  put to death  |strong="4191" srcloc="WLC:2SA.21.4.15" \w* \w  anyone in Israel  |strong="3478" srcloc="WLC:2SA.21.4.16" \w* \w  for us . ”  |srcloc="WLC:2SA.21.4.13" \w* \w  “ Whatever  |strong="4100" srcloc="WLC:2SA.21.4.18" \w* \w  you  |strong="859" srcloc="WLC:2SA.21.4.19" \w* \w  ask ,  |strong="559" srcloc="WLC:2SA.21.4.17" \w* \w  I will do  |strong="6213" srcloc="WLC:2SA.21.4.21" \w* \w  for you , ”  |srcloc="WLC:2SA.21.4.22" \w* \w  he replied .  |strong="559" srcloc="WLC:2SA.21.4.20" \w* \v 5 \w  And they answered  |strong="559" srcloc="WLC:2SA.21.5.1" \w* \w  the king ,  |strong="4428" srcloc="WLC:2SA.21.5.3" \w* \w  “ As for the man  |strong="376" srcloc="WLC:2SA.21.5.4" \w* \w  who  |strong="834" srcloc="WLC:2SA.21.5.5" \w* \w  consumed us  |strong="3615" srcloc="WLC:2SA.21.5.6" \w* \w  and  |strong="834" srcloc="WLC:2SA.21.5.7" \w* \w  plotted  |strong="1819" srcloc="WLC:2SA.21.5.8" \w* \w  against us  |srcloc="WLC:2SA.21.5.9" \w* \w  to exterminate us  |strong="8045" srcloc="WLC:2SA.21.5.10" \w* \w  from existing  |strong="3320" srcloc="WLC:2SA.21.5.11" \w* \w  within any  |strong="3605" srcloc="WLC:2SA.21.5.12" \w* \w  border  |strong="1366" srcloc="WLC:2SA.21.5.13" \w* \w  of Israel ,  |strong="3478" srcloc="WLC:2SA.21.5.14" \w* \v 6 \w  let seven  |strong="7651" srcloc="WLC:2SA.21.6.3" \w* \w  . . .  |strong="582" srcloc="WLC:2SA.21.6.4" \w* \w  of his male descendants  |strong="1121" srcloc="WLC:2SA.21.6.5" \w* \w  be delivered  |strong="5414" srcloc="WLC:2SA.21.6.1" \w* \w  to us  |srcloc="WLC:2SA.21.6.2" \w* \w  so that we may hang them  |strong="3363" srcloc="WLC:2SA.21.6.6" \w* \f + \fr 21.6 \ft Or "expose them" or "execute them"; similar